# boltffi
android/app/src/main/java/io/torvox/bridge/kotlin/

# Golden images — banned. All test verification must use logical assertions
# (pixel values, OCR text output) instead of screenshot comparison.
# See docs/standards/QUALITY-GATE.md for the full policy.
# Suffix-only: already-tracked files are unaffected.
*.mp4
*.png
*.raw

# Font files — banned. Fonts SHALL be installed via Nix (flake.nix).
# See docs/standards/QUALITY-GATE.md for the full policy.
*.ttf
*.otf
*.woff
*.woff2
*.eot
